data.description: Located close to National Harbor close to public transportation. Spacious rooms and plenty of upgrades. Kitchen has been upgraded for an eat-in area. Roof upgraded in '05 and windows replaced in '07. Large fenced backyard comes with storage shed and lovely deck. Sun room in the rear of the house gives added dimension and sunlight.
